ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2003-2004
PrecisAppointment of RODERICK BELL as Ambassador of Canada to the Sultanate of Oman, with residence in Riyadh; LUCIE EDWARDS as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Bhutan, with residence in New Delhi; LOUIS GUAY as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Sao Tomé and Principe, with residence in Libreville; DONALD McLENNAN as Ambassador of Canada to the Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia, with residence in Belgrade; and JULES SAVARIA as Ambassador of Canada to the Central African Republic, with residence in Yaoundé.
